metadata.name: Angliae migrate
metadata.description:
**<><  <><   <><Water world><>   ><> ><>**

This is a world that coexists with marine life. Occasionally, there will be enthusiastic marine life around people, and sometimes magnificent whales will appear in the sky.

`2157*4000 pixel, 300DPI, PNG`




▲**Angliae**
Angliae soars gracefully in the air, she is getting ready to enjoy her vacation in the southern ocean
  
■**Songs Of The Angliae**
Angliae has a beautiful voice, she sings when she is happy, and sometimes sings with her companions, who also have pop songs like us 

●**About humpback whales**
They'll be well fed in the North Pole in summer, (they'll hunt with bubble nets), and in winter they'll migrate near the equator and have fun with friends
